      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Every feature and component functions perfectly, and the engine runs smoothly and quietly. A buyer can expect a vehicle that requires zero maintenance or cosmetic attention, offering a like-new experience in every regard.",
